      • replaceTokens

        public static java.lang.String replaceTokens(java.lang.String string,
                                             Warp warp)
        Replaces all tokens in the given string with the values applicable for the given warp.

        The following tokens are available:

        Token Replacement
        %creator% warp's creator
        %loc% warp's location
        %visits% the warp's visits
        %warp% the warp's name

        Parameters:
        string - the string that contains the tokens
        warp - the Warp whose values should be used as replacement
        Returns:
        the string with replaced tokens

      • replaceTokens

        public static java.lang.String replaceTokens(java.lang.String string,
                                             Warp warp,
                                             Actor actor)
        Replaces all tokens in the given string with the values applicable for the given warp and the given actor.

        The following tokens are available:

        Token Replacement
        %creator% warp's creator
        %loc% warp's location
        %visits% the warp's visits
        %warp% the warp's name
        %actor% the actor's name

        Parameters:
        string - the string that contains the tokens
        warp - the Warp whose values should be used as replacement
        actor - the Actor whose values should be used as replacement
        Returns:
        the string with replaced tokens
